</span><span class='line'>* &gt;0个重复
</span><span class='line'>+ &gt;1个重复
</span><span class='line'>[Gg], [A-Za-z]
</span><span class='line'>\&lt; 单词首
</span><span class='line'>\&gt; 单词尾</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


